{"title":"灾情调查","authors":["韦启美","李村"],"dates":[{"year":1959,"month":12,"day":28}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"灾情调查"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"韦启美画  李村诗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"洪水冲毁龙王庙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把菩萨冲走了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"帝国主义，反动派，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"七嘴八舌哇哇叫："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“中国赤地千里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"共产主义乱糟糟。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"洪水冲毁龙王庙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民公社建高楼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水库清波浪滔滔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"庄稼遍地绿油油，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"龙王庙毁了任它倒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冲走的菩萨无人找。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叫声帝国主义反动派，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是一张灾情调查表："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"泥菩萨，龙王庙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地主，官僚一古脑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"寒风败叶末日到，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"眼看你们通通都难保。（附图片）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“这是今年洪水造成的破坏中唯一没有恢复的，我们也不想恢复它了！”"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}